320
00:28:57,166 --> 00:28:58,000
Tak berdaya.

321
00:28:59,125 --> 00:29:00,458
Tiada makna, ibarat…

322
00:29:02,041 --> 00:29:03,250
menggerakkan kayu.

323
00:29:05,833 --> 00:29:07,458
Kamu lawan siapa dulu?

324
00:29:08,875 --> 00:29:09,708
Manfredi.

325
00:29:14,250 --> 00:29:15,291
Sekejap saja.

326
00:29:16,875 --> 00:29:20,333
Pemain dengan kadar tertinggi
di seluruh negara,

327
00:29:20,416 --> 00:29:23,041
tapi kita di sini, di universiti picisan,

328
00:29:23,125 --> 00:29:27,333
bermain dengan papan plastik murah
dan buah catur plastik murah.

329
00:29:29,083 --> 00:29:31,250
Jika ini kejuaraan golf atau tenis,

330
00:29:31,333 --> 00:29:34,250
kita akan dikelilingi wartawan,
dan bukannya…

331
00:29:35,208 --> 00:29:36,333
entah siapa-siapa.

332
00:29:37,583 --> 00:29:39,666
Lihatlah tempat perlawanan
di Kesatuan Soviet.

333
00:29:39,750 --> 00:29:41,333
Itulah matlamat saya.

